This lab requires that you have a correctly working VPN connection

Sometimes, the lab machine could be busy hence not being able to get to the agent to login.

Prerequisite: You are connected to the OffSec VPN successfully.

Once you click on the play button, that lab machine start to get built - takes about 90 seconds.

Once the lab machine is ready, click on the information icon to see the 

 IP of the machine - that you would type in the browser
 Credentials provided
    Username - you will use to login
    Password - you will use to login

Troubleshooting:

A. Cannot connect to IP address in a browser - connection times out

1. ping the lab machine IP 
2. traceroute the lab machine IP

Success in both of the above means your connection is working.

B. Cannot connect to the IP address in a browser - VPN is connected

1. Connect to port 3000 , type in the browser address bar ipaddress:3000

